{"tid":1900683,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周融曾與確診馬主出席同一婚宴　現於翠雅山房接受隔離","createTime":"2020-02-27T11:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T12:57:31.000Z","uid":6497,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e57d1d3cee09d38413fc1f4d1388b5ed47beac3e","tid":1900683,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/幫港出聲-周融-曾與確診馬主出席同一婚宴-現於翠雅山房接受隔離/?fbclid=IwAR04xqE7m936LOHMnrFm7dRFTMdKFL-RImwq2tpYPsRyNiqe9xF1CBG23U8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%B9%AB%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E8%81%B2-%E5%91%A8%E8%9E%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%A9%9A%E5%AE%B4-%E7%8F%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%BF%A0%E9%9B%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR04xqE7m936LOHMnrFm7dRFTMdKFL-RImwq2tpYPsRyNiqe9xF1CBG23U8&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgeu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=c4436ce8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%B9%AB%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E8%81%B2-%E5%91%A8%E8%9E%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%A9%9A%E5%AE%B4-%E7%8F%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%BF%A0%E9%9B%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR04xqE7m936LOHMnrFm7dRFTMdKFL-RImwq2tpYPsRyNiqe9xF1CBG23U8&h=ee262707\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/幫港出聲-周融-曾與確診馬主出席同一婚宴-現於翠雅山房接受隔離/?fbclid=IwAR04xqE7m936LOHMnrFm7dRFTMdKFL-RImwq2tpYPsRyNiqe9xF1CBG23U8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chowyung-06_iQlEI_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchowyung-06_iQlEI_1200x0.png&h=9f961d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n居於大坑瑞士花園的商人兼馬主周巧兒，前日（25日）確診武漢肺炎。周巧兒於確診前 3 日（22日)，曾於金鐘萬豪酒店出席一場婚禮飯宴，「幫港出聲」召集人周融承認當日亦有出席，現於翠雅山房接受隔離。<br />\n<br />\n周融今日（27日）向《立場新聞》承認，曾於本月 22 日到金鐘萬豪酒店，出席與確診者周巧兒同場的婚禮飯宴，昨日開始於翠雅山房檢疫中心接受隔離，現時未有出現任何病徵。<br />\n<br />\n周融表示：「唔擔心，擔心咩姐，我又冇嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n他指當時兩圍食飯約 20 多人，均是密切接觸者，已接受隔離，全部人沒有任何病徵。他又說「最緊要係自己處之泰然，不要太緊張，靜十多日喺呢到睇吓書。」<br />\n<br />\n確診的周巧兒是周融的侄女，他當日是出席其侄孫的一場婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日於記者會指，周巧兒於本月 22 日出席一個結婚儀式。張竹君說，她早上到位於大坑的竹麗苑參與一對新人的斟荼儀式，然後到北角柏尉山一座參與簽紙儀式，再於金鐘萬豪酒店包廳兩檯食飯。"},{"pid":"91ed4789a711ed96e516f3daf7363fa4abcba16d","tid":1900683,"uid":224510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"日日驗<br />\n驗到陽性為止"},{"pid":"dc2d06356d1e1667e8cab33cb078a41e8c27f115","tid":1900683,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"［行動po 推上熱門thx] 2月29日(六) 毋忘831半周年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1900575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1900575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"500b1645c1c9be98fc6527108e1852ae26de6ba2","tid":1900683,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191f0bad3538cba1eef7634ce5962a2e5badf930","tid":1900683,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b352b71232adde67d10f65a19c7974d07c163d","tid":1900683,"uid":57578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"係咪咁開心先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0269b288a5b158560008aae564d14dedf8c108c","tid":1900683,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"6c85e23ad9dc736e1ff234dab9ee513d6365c39b","tid":1900683,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite